            "title": "比亞迪6 月銷量升半成  半年跌近16%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">比亞迪(01211)公布產銷數據，6月新能源汽車銷量40.35萬輛，按年升5.45%，半年累計報180.85萬輛，按年跌15.72%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/06/img_06aa3434_12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">6 月新能源車產量40.32萬輛，按年升16.86%，首6 月累計產量181.41萬輛，按年跌15.11%。6 月產量91.36萬輛，按年跌14.99%。</p>\n</div>",
